// Example 1: Create thin-walled boss loft with reverse direction wall
// Prerequisites:
// - Two or more closed sketch profiles created on different planes
// - Optionally: guide curves and centerline
// - Select profiles with mark=1, guide curves with mark=2, centerline with mark=4

